data.description: This unique 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom home offers an unparalleled level of comfort and style. Nestled in a charming neighborhood with access to a beach area, private watercraft storage, and a pavilion! Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting foyer that leads to the main living areas. The open concept layout seamlessly combines the living room and kitchen, creating a perfect space for both entertaining and everyday living. The living room boasts large windows that flood the space with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  The main level also hosts a private study, which can be utilized as an office, library, or guest room, depending on your needs. Additionally, there is a 1/2 bathroom on the main level for added convenience. Upstairs, you'll find the master suite. Three additional generously sized bedrooms and a full bathroom complete the upper level. This property also offers a walk-out basement, providing additional living space that can be customized to fit your lifestyle. Step outside onto the deck that overlooks the beautifully landscaped backyard and lake, providing a perfect spot for outdoor gatherings or some morning coffee relaxation. The property also offers a two-car attached garage and spacious driveway for ample parking. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property your new home with just some of your personal touch. Schedule your private showing today and start living your dream lifestyle at 195 Silver Valley Blvd.
